stream.name: The Sofia Bag
stream.description:
Part of the Aspinal Padlock Family and our 2014 Autumn Winter Collection, the Sofia Bag is handmade from the finest tactile deer brown haircalf & smooth deer brown Italian calf leather reflecting the Aspinal signature textural contrast leather frame. Secured by dual leather zip pulls and our signature padlock, the spacious interior is luxuriously lined in shimmering grosgrain and has one main spacious compartment for all your daily essentials, two mobile sized open pockets and fitted with a separate padded iPad / tablet compartment secured by a leather tab closure.

Combining fashion and functionality carry the cleverly designed Sofia Bag by the dual tubular top handles or the eye catching (fully detachable) gold chain-link shoulder strap entwined with plaited calf leather to business meetings or laid-back lunches.

The Sofia Bag arrives in an Aspinal protective felt bag.
